’Ů@6a85098ebdc316def01f37b002f238c2a7450f6b5e7a324833e6ea90b4d3e5b2ÚETitle: title: encode hex
Path: Examples
Content:
Encode a binary value
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 0x[C3 06] | encode hex
C306

```
Encode a string
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> "hello" | encode hex
68656C6C6F

```
Output a Lowercase version of the encoding
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 0x[AD EF] | encode hex --lower
adef

```
